shortBio: Rachel Williams is a talented stand-up comedian hailing from Long Island, New York. She embarked on her comedy journey immediately after graduating from college, and nowadays, you can find her gracing the stages of New York City, delivering laughter to audiences nearly every evening. Rachel has made her mark on the comedy scene, having been featured on SiriusXM, and she was a notable part of the 2022 New York Comedy Festival. Her comedic prowess also shone at the 2023 Rogue Island Comedy Festival, where she was a featured performer.
